      "versionNonce": 1262039,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "What applications see",
      "fontSize": 22,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "What applications see",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 22.5
    },
    {
      "id": "text-1260040",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 784,
      "y": 1291,
      "width": 297,
      "height": 149,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#343a40",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame-1260002",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1261040,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1262040,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Your code usually calls:\n- fetch / HTTP client\n- socket APIs\n- DNS resolver\n\nLower layers are mostly hidden.",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Your code usually calls:\n- fetch / HTTP client\n- socket APIs\n- DNS resolver\n\nLower layers are mostly hidden.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 144
    },
    {
      "id": "rectangle-1260041",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1160,
      "y": 1225,
      "width": 345,
      "height": 235,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "#ebfbee",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame-1260002",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1261041,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1262041,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "text-1260042",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1184,
      "y": 1247,
      "width": 297,
      "height": 27.5,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame-1260002",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1261042,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1262042,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "What OS handles",
      "fontSize": 22,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "What OS handles",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 22.5
    },
    {
      "id": "text-1260043",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1184,
      "y": 1291,
      "width": 297,
      "height": 149,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#343a40",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame-1260002",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1261043,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1262043,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The OS/network stack handles:\n- TCP retransmission\n- ports and sockets\n- IP packet creation\n- routing table lookup",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The OS/network stack handles:\n- TCP retransmission\n- ports and sockets\n- IP packet creation\n- routing table lookup",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 144
    },
    {
      "id": "rectangle-1260044",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 760,
      "y": 1525,
      "width": 345,
      "height": 235,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e67700",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff4e6",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame-1260002",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1261044,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1262044,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "text-1260045",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 784,
      "y": 1547,
      "width": 297,
      "height": 27.5,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e67700",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame-1260002",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1261045,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1262045,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "What routers handle",
      "fontSize": 22,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "What routers handle",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 22.5
    },
    {
      "id": "text-1260046",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 784,
      "y": 1591,
      "width": 297,
      "height": 149,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#343a40",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame-1260002",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1261046,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1262046,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Routers mostly inspect IP headers.\n\nThey forward packets toward\nthe next hop.\n\nThey do not read HTTP bodies.",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Routers mostly inspect IP headers.\n\nThey forward packets toward\nthe next hop.\n\nThey do not read HTTP bodies.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 144
    },
    {
      "id": "rectangle-1260047",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1160,
      "y": 1525,
      "width": 345,
      "height": 235,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#9c36b5",
      "backgroundColor": "#f8f0fc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame-1260002",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1261047,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1262047,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "text-1260048",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1184,
      "y": 1547,
      "width": 297,
      "height": 27.5,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#9c36b5",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame-1260002",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1261048,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1262048,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "What local network handles",
      "fontSize": 22,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "What local network handles",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 22.5
    },
    {
      "id": "text-1260049",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1184,
      "y": 1591,
      "width": 297,
      "height": 149,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#343a40",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame-1260002",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1261049,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1262049,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Switches, Wi-Fi, and Ethernet\nmove frames inside one segment.\n\nARP maps IP addresses\nto MAC addresses.",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Switches, Wi-Fi, and Ethernet\nmove frames inside one segment.\n\nARP maps IP addresses\nto MAC addresses.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 144
    },
    {
      "id": "text-1260050",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 95,
      "y": 1980,
      "width": 1300,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2b8a3e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame-1260002",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1261050,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1262050,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Remember: real systems add caches, proxies, NAT, TLS, CDNs, and load balancers.\nThe stack still explains the path and where each concern fits.",
      "fontSize": 19,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Remember: real systems add caches, proxies, NAT, TLS, CDNs, and load balancers.\nThe stack still explains the path and where each concern fits.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 45
    },
    {
